Class CsvToJsonConverter

java.lang.Object
converter.CsvToJsonConverter
public class CsvToJsonConverter extends Object
Main class responsible for converting data from a CSV file into a structured JSON format. MODIFIED to classify rows as only Item or Document, handle N/A values, and remove generic Artifacts.
